You Are From the Moon

You can vibe with the steady rhythms of the Moon. You're in touch with your emotions and intuition. You possess a great, unmatched imagination - and an infinite memory. Ultra-sensitive, you feel at home anywhere (or with anyone). A total healer, you light the way in the dark for many.
What Planet Are You From?

Today I got laryngitis. I lost my voice and i talk really funny. Jim, Danny, and Kyle were laughing @ me and how i laugh now. :( 

But anyway.. I went to Jims house to get him because we were going to the mall with Danny and Kyle. But Danny is alittle slow and gave me really bad directions. Then after like 20 minutes.. Jim called Kyle and he drove to Farley to meet me. Then we went back to Kyle's house to drop off his car. We were driving down 9W and there was a guy pushing his car into the middle of the street and the light turned green so I beeped @ him and Kyle yelled at him. It was really funny, THat guy was a dumbass. Then we finally got to the mall and we were there for like half an hour but it was boring so we left. We went to brians house and Danielle, Amanda, little Brian, Rob, Ant, Josh, & Nick were there. Amanda is sick too, which really sucks. I hate being sick. Then some people left cause they got bored, & i had to come home cause of the stupid 9:00 law. But now i can rest and hopefully feel better by the end of this weekend.   

oh yeah.. Feel better Amanda :)

You're orange. You're strong and have the reflexes
of a tiger. You're overly protective, and
those skills come in handy... You're a natural
person, with a taste for natural foods (I mean
organic, here.). Well, that's not true.
...Just food in general! You're as
quick-witted as your reflexes, and sometimes
painfully logical. You love wild animals and
pets. (Preferably wild animals!) You're a
natural person, and a true child of Gaia.
You're a stimulating, and outgoing person. You
enjoy making people think, especially with your
infectiously spontaneous attitude. You're a
generally optomistic person, with a love for
showing off all of your good traits. Although
many people may see you as strung-out, or just
plain weird, you're very down-to-earth and
humble. You're incredibly sweet (as this
color's other name!), and you care about people
in general. As this color would describe,
you're energetic beyond all human
comprehension. You've got a nack for drawing,
and you enjoy it, too. When it comes to
school, you're a good listener with an even
better memory. You're studious... At least
when you need to be!

What color are you? (Amazingly detailed & accurate--with pics!)
brought to you by Quizilla

Just got home from Nyack. Me, Jim, Kyle, and Mccormick took the bus to the mall at 5:30 and didn't get there untill about 6:20. We walked to like 3 different stores trying to figure out what we're going to do with the long night ahead of us.. Mccormick said he could get us into a movie but ofcoarse he didn't ..so we decided to walk around more and ponder. We saw Henry with some people so we picked up henry and then went to fye. Jim got a CD and some other little things. Then danny ate chinese food that looked really bad. Then we took a bus to Nyack. We saw Brian and Danielle and went to The Back Door and some really gay band was playing and gave me a headache. We saw Brian K. too and he came also. Then some solo guy came on and read a poem and almost started crying. Then he sang a song that was better then any of those gay bands. He was very very lonely and needed some friends.. i felt really bad for him. Then STF played and thats it. Then we left that gay place and were walking up main street when i saw danielle, melissa, amanda and some other people. Then i left them and then 5 minutes later i saw them again... and then again.. and then they left. So we were all standing outside of planet wings and Brian's mom comes to get us so we all get in the car and there is 8 kids in the car. it was crazy b/c there was cops everywhere. Then i got home and Brian K. came in to say hi to my brother but he was sleeping so Brian went home(he ran home cause the aliens were coming)so yeah that was my day..
http://almightycoconut.livejournal.com/1532.html

*sigh*... ok i've been trying to be happy all day.. and i was mostly in the late afternoon.. but i was upset too.. i just can't stop thinking about stuff... its making my head all jumbled up.. ugh... w/e. I'd go to bed because i am tired.. but i can't sleep cause i can't stop thinking about these things.. this sucks
http://almightycoconut.livejournal.com/1027.html

well.. i just got home from playing pool and eating wendy's .. fun fun fun 

me & becca almost hit another squirrel today.. poor squirrels

me and becca got to alex's house to pick him up and some lady opened the door.. so i was like hi is alex home? and she was like? No?? Sasha?? alex? and i was like Yes! .. and she was like no >:( i was very scared.. then we found alex he was outside walking.. so we left.. never knocking on his door again.. lol 

Ana then comes to my house so me, becca, alex, and ana went to Dara's house to visit her because she was supposed to come with us but had to babysit her brother and his friend. so then we all leave to go back to my house and Josh shows up.. so we go play pool in spring valley ... i was on josh's team and becca is way to good at pool to play any of us.. and ana didn't play either ..so yeah.. 

we decided we were hungry so we went to wendy's..  it was yummy. then i just came home.. and as i'm writing this alex shows up with shaun, some girl and kenny because they were going to try to go bowling again.. but it was closed again.. goddamn bowling alley.. it was craziness.. they just left.  

...The End
http://almightycoconut.livejournal.com/897.html

Ok first Becca came to pick me up and as soon as i got in the car she was like wendy's! and i was like deffinitly!cause we were starving.. then we get to wendy's and there are like 9 cars in the drive through.. so we decided to go inside. We ordered our food and were waiting for 15 minutes for 1 order of goddamn fries because they were cooking!, but we got food for Dara too to surprise her. Then we get to Dara's house and she came outside and we surprised her with all the good food and she was like OH MAN! lol so we went inside and ate our yummy food and then burned some CD's for Becca and we saw Dara's cool rabbit named buttons(so cute) lol. then it shed all over us so we put buttons down. Me and Becca then left because Dara was going driving with her mom. Then me and becca went and picked up some kid Danny that lives near Dara and then me, Becca, and Danny rented Monty Python and the Holy Grail lol it was soo funny. Then we stopped it alittle more than half way through cause it was too long. so yeah.. Becca and me were going to drop Danny off and we see some little kids with a lemonade stand for a big cup of lemonade for 50 cents so we had to stop and get some lol it was really really good. It was PINK lemonade.. not the regular kind... so it was EXTREMELY good. Then we dropped Danny off and then we were going back to my house.. but we passed Brian cause he was skating near my house with Mike.. so we stopped and talked to them alittle while and then Melissa and Rob show up so then me and Becca are supposed to go back to my house for spaghetti and meatballs so i invited Brian to come eat dinner cause my parents like him lol.. so we ate dinner then went to Becca's house and me Becca and Brian went to the park on the river and were playing on the swings and see-saws. So then my dad comes and picks me and Brian up from Becca's and drops Brian off at home. Then i was sitting at home reading a couple chapters of my book and i hear these voices outside my house.. so i'm like wtf? whose here? and its Alex and his friend Shaun.. i didn't even know he knew where i lived? They said they got lost alot.. lol so we were going to go bowling cause Alex has never been bowling before.. but the bowling alley was closed so we went to dunkin doughnuts instead.. we didn't get anything.. so we walked around by alex's house and then they dropped me off home cause they had to go get some kid Tom home.. so yeah that was pretty much my really long day.
http://almightycoconut.livejournal.com/668.html

Well I'm here at Becca's house and we decided to make me a journal. KEWL.. So i guess I'll write about what I did today. Went to school!! So much fun (not).. haha. Then I went over my new bestest friend's house, Becca!! The Joshalator came over and we all took a ride in his blue pick-up truck to Wendy's. We sat in there for about an hour and then we went back to Becca's house. I went to work with her and was offered a job. AWESOME!! Work with Becca!!.. lol.. Now we are just back at her house, listening to AC/DC.. kewl shyt!! I'm off.. everyone add me cuz I'm totally awesome!

P.S. This entire entry was written by Becca..
 AND JOSH IS TAKING EVERYONE TO 6 FLAGS!!! give him $10!!
